description:
This is a complete rewrite of intervalGym. Right now only for the Touchpad but it will be there for all enyo compatible devices soon. The most requested feature to set up different intervals in one training session was the top priority of intervalGym 2. Also the several sound issues where adressed. This version of intervalGym won't interfere with your music. Intervals can be as long or short as you want. There is no lag anymore when playing sounds. 
Since this app is still a BETA you might miss some functions that intervalGym had but they will all be implemented in the next updates. As always input is more then welcome. If you have issues or missing some feature please contact me at any time: mail@j-liebl.de
